<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Thanksgiving Prayer</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Nov 26, 2015 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Gracious Father,
</p>

 <p>
There are those today <br></br>
who struggle to give thanks <br></br>
because of loss, <br></br>
illness, <br></br>
separation, <br></br>
or grief.
</p>

 <p>
May their spirits <br></br>
be comforted with <br></br>
the knowledge that <br></br>
our thoughts and prayers <br></br>
are with them today.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>


